meta.content: An archive of clues and players for Jeopardy! show #7123.

div.div: Some of Alex Trebek's audio was re-recorded when his voice recovered.

td.p: Colby Potter, a policy analyst originally from Denver, Colorado
Jennifer Morgan, an editorial project manager from Southampton, New York
Jonathan Marcus, a law clerk from North Hollywood, California (whose 1-day cash winnings total $20,200)

tr.td: THE NAME OF THE ROSE
WHICH AFRICAN COUNTRY?
TEAMS THAT HAVEN'T WON THE WORLD SERIES
PRESIDENTS' SPEECHES: ONE WORD OFF
A FORTUNE 500 COMPANY
IT'S ALL ABOUT "U"
(Alex: ...because that's the only vowel you will find in each correct response.)
